data.description: Welcome to this beautiful 3 bedroom, 2 bathroom home with 2 car garage beautifully situated on a full quarter acre lot in central Florida. Enjoy the popular characteristics of the open floor plan with high ceilings in the great room and master bedroom. The fully tiled kitchen has granite countertops, subway backsplash tiles, pendant lights and stainless steel appliances. A screened in lanai (20x14) gives you a perfect place to entertain and the huge fenced in backyard is an outdoor lover's dream! Added bonuses to this home are the roof which was replaced in 2018 and HVAC system replaced in 2019. With a gorgeous tree and peaceful easement to the rear and side of this 1232 sq.ft. home, you will find it incredibly cozy and private. Conveniently located around Florida Turnpike in Minneola and easy access to all major roadways, this is the perfect home where privacy and convenience meet. Don't miss this truly extraordinary opportunity!
